hopobject.body: I'm self-employed tamsulosin hydrochloride sustained release capsules The gigantic fund management industry is highly resistant to increased transparency, for obvious reasons. Consumer group Which? looked at the real ongoing costs of several funds and discovered one, for example, where the ongoing charge was quoted as 2.13pc, but where Which? estimated the real, total cost to be more than 4pc. The firm later told Which?, after it pressed for a response, that the actual cost was nearer 2.5pc, still ludicrously high.
